%% State Diagram - Order Life Cycle
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending Payment : Order initiated
    Pending Payment --> Placed (Confirmed) : Payment successful
    Placed (Confirmed) --> Shipped/Delivered : Item is sent/received
    Placed (Confirmed) --> Cancelled : Customer/Store cancels
    Pending Payment --> Cancelled : Customer cancels before payment
    Shipped/Delivered --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]
